{"tid":918261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李卓人：若議會抗爭有多人支持，畀主席趕走能更突出制度嘅不公義！","createTime":"2018-11-27T05:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T05:30:15.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25b4b8e64c916a7a306b95ebd52c6f1e60eff87d","tid":918261,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"面對黃毓民指控，李卓人無奈地說，他出任議事規則委員會一職，是由於當時獲泛民投票支持，「唔係邊個搶邊個嗰位」，而且他認為，事務委員會主席有權驅逐不遵守議事規則的議員離場，根本不會剝削議員抗爭權利，「若果你喺議會抗爭係有好多市民支持，你畀主席趕走，咪更加可以突出制度嘅不公義」。他又相信，仍有不少泛民支持者在議會抗爭之餘，也希望立法會會議可以如常進行，他批評黃毓民和陳偉業不應該將事件上綱上線，表明泛民無意罷免在議會抗爭的議員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110331/15124972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110331%2F15124972&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=758c932c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110331%2F15124972&h=62d823b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110331/15124972</a>"},{"pid":"ab6d09d25b7e286216de85b3dc9c5417c86aeac0","tid":918261,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"要突出阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529df17d06481b0ff3dab55a704de7557528c7d9","tid":918261,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"收皮啦李卓人"}]}